# Geometrical Shapes in Rust

This project was developed as an exercise to help understand the core concepts of Rust, including traits, modules, and image processing. The goal is to implement various geometrical shapes, their associated traits, and a main function that generates a PNG image of random geometrical shapes.
![Geometrical Shapes Example](assets/image.png)

## Table of Contents

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
